Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了個有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是澪前幾天在箱子裡翻出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是以前輕音社的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是哪個年代的樂隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 是…是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對樂隊的印象僅局限於此的我還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還是改一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指頭劃破了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  看著就夠疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪你也看看啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見聽不見看不見聽不見…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我練鼓太多  手上的水泡也磨破啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看…快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊！ 你看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看！ 水泡！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  你有帶繃帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  快看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦  看看啦  小澪  快看看  啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦  很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微借用一下譜架…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們兩個把筆記拿過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消毒真痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指就這樣不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乾淨的桌面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的話很快就會再劃破手指哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多練習幾次以後皮就會硬起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈的時候就不會有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是這樣走過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  老師你有彈過吉他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是以前的朋友啦
