Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  要喝茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好老師啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒…我只是覺得她很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  佐和子老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來你上哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  小澪叫我去申請學園祭的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可輕音社還沒被認可為正規社團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～這樣啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被認可為正規社團？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  貌似是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是湊齊四個社員就沒問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是沒問題了才對啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來既然還沒被認可為正規社團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼隨便使用音樂室好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都沒人說什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦！ 一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  我們還得去問清楚到底是什麼理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？說來澪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小澪的話還在那邊發抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？唯？
