Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  你注意到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼迫弱小社團令其倒閉的學生會陰謀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和其實是個心靈純潔的好孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們不是沒提交社團活動申請書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動申請書？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說過有那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明聽過！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  那還是今年春天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：也有可能是去年秋天或冬天的事情八嘎妹XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長是我！我來寫！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我帶磅蛋糕來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:40.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（磅蛋糕(Pound Cake)：黃油、雞蛋、麵粉和糖的份量各用一磅的蛋糕，又稱牛油蛋糕）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  我要吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  律
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了我就來寫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了我就來寫…就來寫…就來寫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然全都怪你啊——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  小律她也不是故意的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬你太慣她了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦好啦好啦好啦好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙一直都受不了誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這麼縱容她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得輕音社很適合唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你們搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社員四人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧問呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧問？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校的音樂老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她憑著清麗的面孔以及和善的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅在學生當中  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連教師之間也有著很高的人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且演奏技術和歌喉也很出色…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著擁有Fans俱樂部一般的人氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一路上都在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請來做輕音社的顧問老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到顧問啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能來拜託老師你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  雖然我有一百個想給你們當顧問的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在是吹奏樂社的顧問  再兼職的話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止已有無數男人迷倒在她的石榴裙下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說好話也沒用啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會佔用您的時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會自己主動練習的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要寫個名字蓋個章就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也是這裡的畢業生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我看過以前輕音社的相冊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相…相冊在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在音樂室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒料到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的一本相冊竟然保管在學校裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是絕不能令世人所知的血染歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許使其蘇醒於天下的惡魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許過目的封印之書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許打開的禁斷之門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那是…那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你們能看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我以前就在輕音社
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  莫非這個聲音也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你們好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放啦！太丟人啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見聽不見…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒走出陰影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  那吉他也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦！彈一下！彈一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這桃花心木和楓木製Les Paul的獨特重量感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:51.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Les Paul：Gibson知名品牌，以傳奇吉他手，多軌錄音的發明者Les Paul命名。）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這Hum-bucking Pickup帶有優美失真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Hum-bucking Pickup：1955年Gibson發明的一種雙線圈封閉式拾音器，1957年被使用\N到了Les Paul型號上，音色渾厚，非常適合玩搖滾和金屬。拾音器（Pickup）是將\N樂器自身的弦等振動轉化為電訊號的裝置）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（失真（Distortion）：一種特殊音效，失真是將輸入的訊號進行處理，並加入了\N原來沒有的頻率，這一般會令聲音聽起來更熱烈高亢）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛音豐富的柔潤音色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（泛音（Harmonics）：弦樂器演奏中常用的一種別具特色的奏法，以基音\N為標準，其餘各部分也是同時振動，就是泛音。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神變了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速彈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點弦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（點弦（tapping）：一種將手指按觸在指板的弦上橫向彈奏\N而發出快速且連續性音效的技巧）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用牙彈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我的吉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小娘兒們！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂室可不是你家豬圈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…都看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明決定做老師時要保持淑女形象的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是八年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：也有可能是九年前或十年前的事了八嘎妹XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就進入回憶模式啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:11:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比較喜歡狂野一點的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為他喜歡的那種女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加地狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Level：NANA）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加地…更加地…狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Level：Dir en grey）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加地…更加地…更加地！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Level：Slipknot）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂野  狂野  狂野！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我交往也不是不可以啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也就那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  安慰我的話就不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  抬起頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被揭穿的話就請當顧問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  好一個靠得住的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像在發呆哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種感覺的原創曲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？以顧問的標準來說？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…搶拍和拖拍等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有節奏部分也有點散亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有很多在意的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但首先  沒有主唱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  該不會連歌詞都還…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你們就這樣還想在學園祭出場演出啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們佔領音樂室這麼久都在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可不是茶館啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…來點蛋糕好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  早點寫歌詞就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老師能夠成為我們的顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得興奮得心怦怦地跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫歌詞也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「心怦怦地跳」…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫好了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  現在就？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你那句現在算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但我還是很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  不會笑你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等不了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶過來不就是要給我們看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一點～點  悄悄～地給我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好狡猾  要看的話也是我最先嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是社長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是澪的知心摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是澪的知心摯友2號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威風什麼  我可是澪心靈的歸宿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（澪：你們都是我的翅膀！XD  by dj）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候成歸宿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄉下的奶奶身體還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  現在沒在說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  去年我寄賀年卡了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我打岔！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊給我看！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何如何～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「每當注視著你時  我的Heart」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「怦怦★地跳」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp180}　{\fsp1}Marshmallow{\r}\N「搖曳的思念  好似棉花糖一般」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「軟軟★呼呼」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想撕碎這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我倒是覺得這個寫得感覺不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  稍稍特色了一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  唯你也來說兩句…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡哦  這個歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬…紬你怎麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超陶醉狀態！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧  連紬也喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:16:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和覺得這個歌詞不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個再重新考慮一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先請冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說喜歡這種活潑的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的形象也許會提升呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  您真年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是佐和子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老師  太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子～佐和子～佐和子～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也喜歡～這個曲子～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就按照這個歌詞來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是澪你就是主唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼難為情的歌詞我唱不了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  作者！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  澪不行的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬你來試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我光是鍵盤就已經盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…唯  你要試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我唱歌並不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道我能不能勝任…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  開玩笑的  我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唱  我想唱啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你來唱唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「每當注視著你時  我的Heart…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得一邊彈吉他一邊唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對呀  忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這次把歌給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈著吉他我就唱不了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來給你做特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先教你怎麼用牙來彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  別被我甩掉了跟上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會對佐和子老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她對佐和子老師啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  你喜歡佐和子老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得女孩子們之間真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要本人們願意的話  沒什麼不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  啊…  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：澪乃總有一天也會明白的XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  主唱是唯  曲名叫做「軟軟呼呼Time」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那麼演出時間決定後我再來通知你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意跑來一趟  謝謝你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是學生會的工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  用唯真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上週起一放學就在佐和子老師家裡做特訓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還趕得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  小唯  讓她們見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確提升了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是充滿自信的表情！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「每當注視著你時  我的Heart怦怦★地跳…」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練得太多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗓子啞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們賣萌也沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那主唱怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要換的話只有今日之內了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  小澪的話應該記得歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作詞者本人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破鑼嗓子唯也拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:21:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離出場  還有三天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:16.63,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だって本当はcrazy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:21.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}白鳥たちはそう　見えないとこでバタ足するんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:27.23,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}本能に従順 忠実　翻弄も重々承知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:32.71,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前途洋々だし…だからたまに休憩しちゃうんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:43.43,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}近道あればそれが王道　はしょれる翼もあれば上等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:53.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ヤバ 爪割れた　グルーで補修した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:58.50,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}それだけでなんか達成感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:03.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大事なのは自分　かわいがること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:09.78,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分を愛さなきゃ　他人も愛せない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:12.97,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:15.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だって本当はcrazy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:20.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能ある鷹はそう　見えないとこにピック隠すんです
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:26.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想像に一生懸命　現実は絶体絶命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.96,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}発展途中だし…だから不意にピッチ外れるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:16.63,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因為其實是crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:21.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}白鳥們在暗處淺打水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:27.23,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}忠實順從本能　明知重重顛簸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:32.71,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前途光明…所以稍事休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:43.43,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}近道即王道　折翼更上等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:53.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}利爪破裂　以膠修補
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:58.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如此就有成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:03.80,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}憐惜自己很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:09.78,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不愛自己何談愛他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:12.97,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:15.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因為其實是crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:20.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能樂者斂其鋒芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:26.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拼命想像　現實卻一籌莫展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}還在發展途中…所以能意外地擺脫危機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式出演前不再練習一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉  現在脫不開身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還算有些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再練習一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要練習
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來沒事 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是正式演出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去抓緊練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習啊…
